01:00:44.319 --> 01:00:52.510
experience of an amputated body part, hence,
phantom limb. It's a really wonderful term.

01:00:52.510 --> 01:00:55.150
\
Anyway, she talked to people with phantom

01:00:55.150 --> 01:01:02.499
limb, amputees obviously but phantom limb
and asked them what their experience of this

01:01:02.499 --> 01:01:09.969
phantom limb was like. And then she digitally
created that experience in the photographs.

01:01:09.969 --> 01:01:18.279
So for example, there is a picture that I
