01:01:38.799 --> 01:01:44.999
to see that and it's one of the few places
that I have seen the subjective experience

01:01:44.999 --> 01:01:50.089
of disability represented visually. So it's
really interesting stuff. \

01:01:50.089 --> 01:01:56.359
